exceptions.exn: In environment x, y : Rbar H : Rbar_lt y x Unable to unify "match ?M2443 with | Finite a => locally a (fun u : R => Rbar_lt u ?M2444) | p_infty => exists M : R, forall x : R, M < x -> (fun u : R => Rbar_lt u ?M2444) x | m_infty => exists M : R, forall x : R, x < M -> (fun u : R => Rbar_lt u ?M2444) x end" with "match x with | Finite a => locally a (fun u : R => Rbar_lt y u) | p_infty => exists M : R, forall x : R, M < x -> (fun u : R => Rbar_lt y u) x | m_infty => exists M : R, forall x : R, x < M -> (fun u : R => Rbar_lt y u) x end".
In environment x, y : Rbar H : Rbar_lt y x Unable to unify "Rbar_lt y x" with "Rbar_locally x (fun u : R => Rbar_lt y u)".

original: intros x y H. apply open_Rbar_lt'. apply H.
